title: Durham will tell residents to stay home amid virus outbreak
description: DURHAM, N.C. (AP) — North Carolina's fourth-largest city planned Wednesday to join a number of local jurisdictions issuing stay-at-home orders to slow the spread of COVID-19.
content:
DURHAM, N.C. (AP) North Carolina's fourth-largest city planned Wednesday to join a number of local jurisdictions issuing stay-at-home orders to slow the spread of COVID-19.
